anations for some of the critical business and policy issues you’ve often wondered about, as well as for others you haven’t yet considered.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Insurance / Health.2bisacsh1 aFinkelstein, Amy, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aFisman, Ray, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311074978640uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300268553?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300268553423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300268553/original  a978-3-11-074978-6  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY